---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`About · ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="About Nico Neumann and this site." />
		<style>
			.page-head {
				margin: 0 0 2.5em 0;
			}
			.page-head h1 {
				margin: 0 0 0.25em 0;
				font-size: 2rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				letter-spacing: -0.02em;
			}
			h2 {
				margin: 2em 0 0.5em 0;
				font-size: 1.05rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				color: var(--ink);
			}
			p {
				line-height: 1.65;
				color: var(--ink);
				font-size: 15px;
				max-width: 60ch;
			}
			ul {
				margin: 0 0 1.25em 0;
				padding-left: 1.2em;
				color: var(--ink);
				font-size: 14.5px;
				line-height: 1.65;
			}
			.lede {
				color: var(--ink-muted);
				font-size: 1rem;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<section class="page-head">
				<h1>About</h1>
				<p class="lede">
					I'm Nicolas Neumann (Nico). I build with AI agents, ship products, and document the
					journey here. Two feeds:
				</p>
			</section>
			<ul>
				<li><a href="/journal/">Journal</a>: daily entries, hours worked, what shipped, lessons.</li>
				<li><a href="/posts/">Posts</a>: longer-form building-in-public writing, milestones, decisions.</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>Why this exists</h2>
			<p>
				Three reasons. First, as proof-of-self: a documented track record I can hand to investors,
				collaborators, or anyone who wants to know whether I show up consistently and think
				clearly. Second, as a way to stay in touch with friends, family, and people I'd otherwise
				lose track of. Third, because writing the work down forces me to understand it.
			</p>

			<h2>How this site is built</h2>
			<p>
				Astro + MDX, hosted on Cloudflare Pages, content authored through Claude Code. The entire
				publishing pipeline runs through the same AI agent harness I use to build the rest of my
				products. Meta, in the good way.
			</p>

			<h2>Get in touch</h2>
			<p>
				Email: <a href="mailto:neumanic2@gmail.com">neumanic2@gmail.com</a>.
				Also on
				<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/nicolas-neumann-520736286/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>,
				<a href="https://github.com/akkton" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>, and
				<a href="https://www.instagram.com/nickswagster/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
